---
// Core principle banner displayed below the hero
---

<div class="principle-banner">
  <div class="principle-banner-icon">💡</div>
  <div class="principle-banner-text">
    <strong>Core Principle:</strong> The agent sees only the repository. Everything not accessible
    in-context effectively does not exist. This plan encodes knowledge into the repo so agents can
    operate autonomously.
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .principle-banner {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent-light), var(--teal-light));
    border-bottom: 1px solid #bae6fd;
    padding: 18px 64px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
  }
  .principle-banner-icon {
    font-size: 22px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .principle-banner-text {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #0c4a6e;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .principle-banner-text strong {
    font-weight: 700;
  }
</style>
